query:
SELECT s.id, s.name, a.trainingRestrictions, a.muscleEmphasis, a.cardioActivities, a.mainGoal, a.exerciseExperience, a.injuries, a.medications
FROM students s 
LEFT JOIN anamneses a ON s.id = a.studentId 
WHERE s.name LIKE '%Laura%' 
LIMIT 1;
